'Yan majalisa na Wales da ke tsoron kunya
An samu rudani tsakanin wasu 'yan majalisa game da shawarar da aka bayar na sauya sunan wakilin majalisa na Wales daga AM (Member of the Welsh Parliament) zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan ya sa aka fara shirin sauya sunan majalisar dokokin Wales.
'Yan majalisa na kowane jam'iyya na siyasa suna fargabar cewa wannan zai haifar da abin da ba shi da kyau.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Labour ya ce yana da damuwa cewa jam'iyyar za ta shiga cikin "Twp" da "Pwp".
Don masu karatu da ba na Welsh ba, Twp na Welsh yana nufin "m" kuma Pwp na nufin "ƙazanta".
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Pride Kamli ya ba da shawarar wani madadin saboda jam'iyyar duka ba ta gamsu ba.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Conservative Party ta Wales ya ce, "Ko da yake jam'iyyar ta kasance 'a bude' game da canjin sunan, ba ta da bambanci sosai a yadda ake furta MWP da 'muppet' ".
A cikin harshen Welsh, "w" yana kama da "u" a harshen Turanci na Yorkshire.
Kwamitin 'yan majalisa da ke shirin tsara sabon sunan, ya ce: "Samun yanke shawara na karshe game da sunan 'yan majalisa, ba shakka, al'amarin da ya kamata a ba da shawara ga 'yan majalisa da kansu".
