LeBron, Lakers za su fara wasa a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
LeBron James zai fara buga wasan farko a Los Angeles Lakers da magoya bayansa ke jira.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma ba mu san minti nawa zai yi wasa ba.
"Zai wuce minti daya da kasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Mike Trudell, mai ba da rahoto a Lakers ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai buga wasa ne na iyakantaccen lokaci.
Bayan atisayen da suka yi a farkon makon, an tambayi James game da jadawalin wasanni shida na kakar wasan Lakers.
"A wannan lokaci na aikina, ba na bukatar wasannin farko don shirya kakar wasa", in ji shi.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya faru a lokacin da aka yi wa Trump yaƙi a West Virginia.
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron zabensa a wannan daren daga garin Wheeling da ke jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko na tarurruka biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da wuraren da ke da alaka da Trump, kamar su Tennessee da Mississippi.
A yanzu da ake jiran zaben amincewa da nadin babban alkalin kotun, Trump na neman karfafa goyon baya ga zaben da ke tafe, saboda 'yan jam'iyyar Republican na cikin hatsarin rasa rinjaye a majalisa a zaben watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne taron Trump na yammacin Virginia zai gudana, kuma ta yaya za mu iya kallon sa a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wiring, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne a yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018, da karfe 7:00 na yamma (lokacin Gabas).
Za a iya kallon wasan kwaikwayon na Trump a West Virginia a kan YouTube a kan:
Yayin da FBI ke binciken zargin cin zarafin da ake yi wa dan takarar kujerar babban alkalin kotun Burt Kavanaugh, kuma an dage zaben amincewa da nadin a majalisar dattawa har mako guda, Trump na iya yin tsokaci game da sauraron Kavanaugh na wannan makon.
Amma babban dalilin wannan taro da ake yi a kullum shi ne don karfafa ƙarfin jam'iyyar Republican da ke fuskantar mawuyacin yanayi a zaben watan Nuwamba.
A cewar Reuters, wannan shine dalilin da ya sa jam'iyyar Trump ta ce taron na mako biyar na gaba yana nufin "karfafa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya don kiyaye da kuma fadada rinjayen 'yan Republican a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Wakilai. "
"Samun rinjaye a majalisa na da matukar muhimmanci ga manufofinsa, don haka shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da yawa a lokacin kakar zaben", in ji mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda ya nemi a boye sunansa.
A cewar Metro News na West Virginia, taron da aka shirya a West Bank Arena a Wheeling na iya "tarar da magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a iya buga shi a kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh".
Trump ya lashe zaben West Virginia a 2016 da kashi 40 cikin dari, amma ziyarar da zai kai kasar a ranar Asabar ita ce ta biyu da Trump zai kai a cikin wata guda.
Trump yana neman goyon bayan dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia Patrick Morrissey wanda ke bayan zaben.
Simon Heder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia ya ce, "shiga wurin shugaban kasa don ya goyi bayan shi ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrissey ba", in ji Reuters.
