A shekarar 2007 rundunar sojin ruwa ta ba da umarnin jiragen ruwa guda hudu, na Barden-Würtenberg, wanda zai maye gurbin jiragen ruwan Bremen da ke tsufa a yanzu.
Barden-Würtenberg-class frigate jirgin ruwa ne, ban da iko cannon, anti-air makamai masu linzami da anti-jirgin ruwan makamai masu linzami, an kuma nuna cewa an haɗa da stealth fasaha kamar rage radars, infrared sigina da kuma sauti sigina.
